leve.name: The Doom that Came to Belah'dia
leve.description: It draws breath still, the Invisible City, though the time of Belah'dia is long past. Do you not hear the stones that shroud the ruins, hear them turning? Click-click-click like a restless dog pacing its master's chamber floor. Bring them away, I beg you, thin the herd. The power, it grows.
leve.client: Order of Nald'thal Bishop, Lilimolu Gigimolu
